title: Castro flanks new Cuban leader at May Day rally
text:
Castro flanks new Cuban leader at May Day rally Wednesday, May 02, 2018 - 01:06
In a show of continuity, Raul Castro stood side-by-side with his protege Miguel Diaz-Canel during Havana's May Day march on Tuesday. Nathan Frandino reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
